Subject: [PATCH] Modify systemd manager for OpenWrt support

Refactor systemd manager for OpenWrt compatibility by bypassing systemd checks and using ubus for service management.
---
 agent/systemd.go | 265 +++++++++++++++++------------------------------
 1 file changed, 94 insertions(+), 171 deletions(-)

